    <item>
      <title>Mirae Asset 的 Fok 谈中国市场和 ETF 策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/mirae-asset-s-fok-on-china-markets-etf-strategy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[未来资产全球投资（香港）ETF 投资组合管理主管 Dennis Fok 讨论了香港和中国股票市场以及未来资产的 ETF 策略。他在“彭博：中国秀”节目中与 David Ingles 和 Yvonne Man 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/mirae-asset-s-fok-on-china-markets-etf-strategy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:14:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管美联储大幅降息，日元兑美元汇率仍跌至 145</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/yen-weakens-to-145-against-dollar-despite-jumbo-fed-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元跌至9月初以来的最低水平，因为即使美联储降息后，收益率差距缩小的速度仍不确定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/yen-weakens-to-145-against-dollar-despite-jumbo-fed-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新世界考虑更换亿万富翁继承人担任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/new-world-weighs-replacing-billionaire-heir-cheng-as-ceo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新世界发展公司在彭博社报道该公司正考虑更换第三代继承人郑志刚担任首席执行官后，该公司暂停了在香港的股票交易。此前，该公司因减记导致 20 年来首次出现年度亏损。彭博社企业集团和媒体记者 Shirley Zhao 在“彭博社：中国秀”节目中与 Yvonne Man 讨论了相关细节。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/new-world-weighs-replacing-billionaire-heir-cheng-as-ceo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:07:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>预知未来并不会让你赚钱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-09-26/knowing-the-future-won-t-make-you-money</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使交易员已经知道明天的消息，他们仍然可能表现不佳。真正重要的是他们下注多少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-09-26/knowing-the-future-won-t-make-you-money</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:03:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顶级银行家通过投奔私人信贷机构来追逐巨额利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/private-credit-firms-are-poaching-some-of-wall-street-s-top-loan-bankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越来越多的杠杆融资银行家跳槽到私人资本公司，以寻求更大的财富和在蓬勃发展的市场中工作的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/private-credit-firms-are-poaching-some-of-wall-street-s-top-loan-bankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的 Jewell 表示，股票可以应对盈利下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/blackrock-s-jewell-says-stocks-can-cope-with-earnings-downgrades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司的海伦·朱厄尔 (Helen Jewell) 表示，尽管今年剩余时间全球企业盈利预期看似乐观，但股市目前可能能够吸收适度的下调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/blackrock-s-jewell-says-stocks-can-cope-with-earnings-downgrades</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PGIM：全球投资者更加关注地缘政治风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/pgim-global-investors-more-focused-on-geopolitical-risk-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PGIM 总裁兼首席执行官 David Hunt 表示，地缘政治仍然是首席信息官和投资者最关心的问题，而非传统的商业周期问题。他在私募股权活动 SuperReturn Asia 的间隙与 Haslinda Amin 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/pgim-global-investors-more-focused-on-geopolitical-risk-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:58:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑向顶级银行注资 1420 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/china-weights-142b-capital-injection-into-top-banks-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，中国正考虑向其最大的国有银行注入 1 万亿元人民币或 1420 亿美元资本，以提高其放贷能力。彭博社中国通讯员 Minmin Low 与 Yvonne Man 和 David Ingles 在“彭博社：中国秀”节目中讨论了细节。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/china-weights-142b-capital-injection-into-top-banks-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:46:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚央行认为林吉特将获得“持久支持”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/malaysia-s-central-bank-sees-enduring-support-for-ringgit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚央行表示，鉴于马来西亚良好的经济前景和改革，林吉特的涨势可能持续下去。本周，林吉特攀升至三年来的最高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/malaysia-s-central-bank-sees-enduring-support-for-ringgit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
